<section class="brand--ministry-of-defence brand__border-color organisation__brand-border-top organisation__section-wrap organisation__margin-bottom" id="what-we-do">
  <div class="grid-row">
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--padding gem-c-heading--margin-bottom-2  ">What the Military Aviation Authority does</h2>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid-row">
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak " data-module="govspeak">
    
          <p></p>
<div class="govspeak">
<p>The Military Aviation Authority is responsible for the regulation, surveillance and assurance of the defence air operating and technical domains.</p>

<p><abbr title="Military Aviation Authority">MAA</abbr> is part of the <a class="brand__color" href="/government/organisations/ministry-of-defence">Ministry of Defence</a> and the <a class="brand__color" href="/government/organisations/defence-safety-authority">Defence Safety Authority</a>.</p>
</div>

          <p>
            <a href="/government/organisations/military-aviation-authority/about" class="brand__color">
              Read more about what we do
            </a>
          </p>

</div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>



